---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="What's Next - VOLI"
  description="The VOLI roadmap: announcements, upcoming features, and what we're building next for professional and college volleyball fans."
  activePage="whats-next"
>
    <main class="card">
        <h1 class="title">What's Next</h1>
        <p class="lead">A look at what we're building, what's launching, and where VOLI is headed.</p>

        <div class="placeholder">
            <span class="placeholder-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <p>We're putting this page together — soon it'll be the home for announcements, feature updates, and our public roadmap.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-label">Latest Announcement</div>
            <div class="announcement-card">
                <span class="announcement-pill">Coming 2026</span>
                <h2 class="announcement-title">NCAA Women's Fantasy Volleyball</h2>
                <p class="announcement-body">We're expanding VOLI's fantasy platform to NCAA Division I women's volleyball for the 2026 season. More details — draft format, league sizes, scoring, and signup — coming soon.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 5rem 2rem 2rem;
        padding-top: calc(5rem + env(safe-area-inset-top));
    }

    .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--glass-highlight), transparent);
    }

    .title {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .lead {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .placeholder {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        background: rgba(200, 255, 0, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(200, 255, 0, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .placeholder-dot {
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--accent);
        flex-shrink: 0;
        animation: pulseDot 1.6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .placeholder p {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
    }

    @keyframes pulseDot {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        50% { opacity: 0.55; transform: scale(0.8); }
    }

    .section {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-label {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .announcement-card {
        padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        border-radius: 16px;
    }

    .announcement-pill {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(200, 255, 0, 0.18), rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.12));
        border: 1px solid rgba(200, 255, 0, 0.35);
        border-radius: 100px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    }

    .announcement-title {
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 650;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    }

    .announcement-body {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        body { padding: 6rem 1rem 1rem; }
        .card { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 20px; }
        .title { font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .lead { font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .announcement-title { font-size: 1.05rem; }
    }
</style>
